data.description: Rare 1-story in amazing Keller neighborhood. This property is ready to go! Well maintained brick home in the heart of Keller ISD.  Current owner uses 4 bedrooms but could easily be 3 bedrooms and Large Study.  Large family room with covered patio out back door.  Master Bath has complete upgrade with new vanity, floors, tub and shower. Kitchen upgraded with granite and custom cabinets.  New water heater.  New AC in 2019. This property is move-in ready for borrowers that need a quick close! Neighborhood has rear alley for driveways and parking.
